#. type: Title =
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "ZoneMapper: Adjusting brightness\n"
msgstr "ゾーン マッパー: 輝度の調整\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:5
msgid "[3 of 8](Tool-ZoneMapper-Exposure.html)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:8
msgid ""
"One of several adjustments you can make to your photo using the ZoneMapper "
"tool is brightness."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:12
msgid ""
"\"Brightness\" is what is perceived as the tonal range starting from the "
"highest highlights down to the midtones. Your photo can be adjusted to "
"appear brighter without increasing exposure by lifting up the midtones."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "To increase the brightness of your photo:\n"
msgstr "写真の輝度を上げるには:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:17
msgid "![image](images/Button-ZoneMapper.png)"
msgstr "![image](images/Button-ZoneMapper.png)"

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:27
msgid ""
"Click the ZoneMapper tool button in the [tool bar](Tools-Editing.html). (A "
"new ZoneMapper tool will appear at the top of the [tool "
"stack](Tool_Stack.html).)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:27
msgid ""
"Move the mouse along the zones in the ZoneMapper to approximately the middle "
"zone."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '3.  '
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:27
msgid ""
"Click between two zones. A *zone lock* will appear (a thin, blue line with a "
"little 'X' at its right)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '4.  '
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:27
msgid "Drag the zone lock upwards. As you do so, your photo will get brighter."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      ----------------------------------------------------------- -- "
"----------------------------------------------------------\n"
"      (a) before                                                     (b) "
"after\n"
"      ![image](images/Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness-before-en.png)      "
"![image](images/Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness-after-en.png)\n"
"      ----------------------------------------------------------- -- "
"----------------------------------------------------------\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:39
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"5.  Optionally:\n"
"    -   Create a mask using [regions](Regions.html).\n"
"    -   Select a different [blend mode](Blend_Modes.html).\n"
"    -   Adjust the [Opacity slider](Tool_Anatomy.html#Opacity).\n"
"    -   Make a [color/luminosity](Color_Luminosity_Selection.html)\n"
"        selection.\n"
msgstr ""
"5.  Optionally:\n"
"    -   Create a mask using [regions](Regions.html).\n"
"    -   Select a different [blend mode](Blend_Modes.html).\n"
"    -   Adjust the [Opacity slider](Tool_Anatomy.html#Opacity).\n"
"    -   Make a [color/luminosity](Color_Luminosity_Selection.html)\n"
"        selection.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '6.  '
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:41
msgid "To delete a zone lock, click the little 'X' at its right."
msgstr "ゾーン ロックを解除するには、右側の小さな　'X' をクリックします。"

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "    ![image](images/Tool-ZoneMapper-X.png)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Tool-ZoneMapper-Brightness.markdown.txt:46
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Note:** To decrease the brightness of you photo, drag the zone lock\n"
"downwards rather than upwards.\n"
msgstr ""

